{
  "chapter": "129",
  "title": "货殖列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "老子小国寡民论",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">老子</span>说：“治理得最完美的时候，邻国相望，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸡</span>鸣<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狗</span>吠的声音彼此听得见；<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众各自觉得饭食甘美、衣服漂亮、风俗安适、职业可乐，直到老死也不相互往来。”可是后世要真把这种样子作为施政的目标，非得堵住<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众的耳目不可——这几乎是行不通的。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "太史公论经济源流",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">神农</span>以前的情形，我不清楚。从<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">诗书</span>所记的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">虞</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>以来，人人都想让耳目尽情享受声色，嘴巴尝遍所有美味，身子图安逸享乐，心里又要夸耀权势和才干——这种风俗浸染<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>间已经很久了。就算挨家挨户给人讲精妙的道理，也没法叫他们改过。所以治理的上策，是顺其自然；其次是加以引导；再次是教诲开导；再次是整顿规范；最下下策是与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>争利。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "四方物产与自然之道",
      "text": "说到天下物产：<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山西</span>盛产木材、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">竹</span>、穀树、纑麻、旄牛尾、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玉石</span>；<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>多<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鱼</span>、盐、漆、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">丝</span>、声色歌舞；<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江南</span>盛产棻、梓、姜、桂、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>、锡、连（铅矿）、丹沙、犀角、玳瑁、珠玑、齿革；<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">龙门</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">碣石</span>以北多<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">羊</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">旃</span>裘、筋角；铜、铁则广布于<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>之间的山中，像棋子一样散布。——这是大致情况。都是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人民</span>所喜爱、人们用作衣食、养生送死的必需品。所以要等待农民种出来，虞人开采出来，工匠制造出来，商人流通出来——这难道还用得着政令征发、会期会合吗？人各凭所能、尽其力，以求得所欲的东西。所以：物贱了正是求贵的征象，贵了正是求贱的征象；各劝其业、乐其事，就像水往低处流一样，日夜不停，不召自来，不求自出。这难道不合于道、不合于自然吗！"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "农工商虞四民与管仲治齐",
      "text": "<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">周书</span>说：“农夫不产，粮食就缺；工匠不产，器物就缺；商人不通三宝（粮食、器物、财货），那一环就断；虞人不开发，财货就短缺。”财货短缺，山泽就开发不出。这四样行业，是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>人衣食的源头。源头大的，就富庶；源头小的，就贫乏。往上可以富国，往下能富家——贫富的道理，不是谁能抢走或送来的，巧的人就丰余，笨的人就不足。所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太公望</span>封在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">营丘</span>，那地方盐碱不生、人又少；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太公</span>就劝女子纺织、鼓励工巧、开通鱼盐，于是人物归聚，络绎不绝如钱币串成串，车轮辐条向毂合拢。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的冠带衣履流行<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，东海到泰山之间的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都整理衣袖去齐国朝拜。后来齐国一度中衰，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管子</span>再加修治，设立九府，于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓公</span>称霸，九合<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，一匡<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">管氏</span>也身兼大夫，地位超过了列国的国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>。所以齐国的富足强盛，一直延续到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">威</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">宣</span>之世。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "富与礼义天下熙攘",
      "text": "所以说：“仓廪充实才懂<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼节</span>，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>食充足才知荣辱。”<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>生于富而废于贫。所以<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">君子</span>富了，就喜欢施德行义；小人富了，就量力而行。水深鱼就来生息，山深兽就来栖息——人富了，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">仁义</span>就来附他。富人得势更显耀，失势门客便散；人一散，便不乐。这道理在<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">夷狄</span>那里更明显。谚语说：“<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千金</span>之家的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>弟，不会死在市集上。”这不是空话。又说：“<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>熙熙，皆为利来；<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>攘攘，皆为利往。”连<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千乘</span>的王、<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万家</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">侯</span>、<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百室</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，都还以贫穷为忧患，何况是编入户籍的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">匹夫</span>百<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>呢！"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "计然七策越国致富",
      "text": "从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">越王句践</span>被围在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>山上，启用了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">计然</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">计然</span>给他出主意：“懂得要打仗，就得整修兵甲；懂得物资的时用，就得明白货物——这两样摸清了，万种货物的行情也就看得清了。所以岁星行到<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span>位，丰收；到<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">水</span>位，歉收；到<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">木</span>位，饥荒；到<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">火</span>位，干旱。旱年就备<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">舟</span>船，水年就备<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>马——这是事物的规律。大致<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">六年（时长）</span>丰、<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">六年（时长）</span>旱、<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十二年（时长）</span>便有一次大饥荒。米价若低到每石<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十</span>钱，农夫吃亏；若高到每石<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">九十</span>钱，商人吃亏。商人吃亏财货就不流通，农夫吃亏田地就荒废。上限不过每石<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八十</span>钱，下限不下<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十</span>钱，则农商都得利——平价<span class=\"verb-economic\" title=\"经济动词\">粜</span>米来调齐物价，关市货物不匮乏，这才是治国之道。<span class=\"verb-economic\" title=\"经济动词\">积</span>储的要诀：货物要保全品质，钱币不要闲置；货物互相<span class=\"verb-economic\" title=\"经济动词\">贸</span>易，容易腐烂的不要囤积，不要赌价。衡量所储多寡，就晓得贵贱：贵到极处便跌，贱到极处便涨。贵了，就要像扔<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">粪土</span>一样抛出去；贱了，就要像收<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">珠玉</span>一样收进来——<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">财币</span>要让它流动得像流水。”这策略推行了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十年（时长）</span>，国家富强，厚赏<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>；士兵迎着箭<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">石</span>冲锋，像渴了找水喝一般。越国就这样报了强<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>之仇，威震<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>，名列“<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五霸</span>”之一。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "范蠡陶朱致富",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">范蠡</span>既已洗刷了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>之耻，长叹一声：“<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">计然</span>的策略一共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七</span>条，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>国只用了其中<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五</span>条就得偿所愿。既然已经施行在国家上，我想把它拿来治家。”于是他乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">扁舟</span>漂浮于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江湖</span>之上，改名换姓：到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国化名<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鸱夷子皮</span>，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陶</span>地化名<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">硃公</span>看<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陶</span>这地方是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之中，和各方<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>四通八达，货物在此集散，于是置办产业，囤货居奇；顺时逐利，不苛责于人。所以善于治生的人，既能选人，又能择时。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十九年（时长）</span>之中，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三</span>次<span class=\"verb-economic\" title=\"经济动词\">致</span>积<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千金</span>，两次把所积全<span class=\"verb-economic\" title=\"经济动词\">散</span>给贫困的朋友和远房兄<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟</span>——这就是所谓“富而好行其德”的人。后来他年老力衰，生意就交给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>孙去办。子孙能承父志，把家业越做越大，终至巨万。所以人们说到富翁，都要数<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陶硃公</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "子贡廉贾显名",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：子贡\">子赣（子贡）</span>在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">仲尼</span>门下学成之后，从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>国的仕途上退下，在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">曹</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>之间贩卖<span class=\"verb-economic\" title=\"经济动词\">鬻</span>货。孔门<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">七十子</span>的学生里，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：子贡\">赐（子贡）</span>最富。另一位<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">原宪</span>连糟糠都吃不饱，住在偏僻的陋巷里；子贡则四马驾车、骑从一大群，带着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">束帛</span>厚礼去聘问<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。他所到之处，国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>没有一位不跟他分庭抗礼的。使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>的名声传遍<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的，前后都是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">子贡</span>辅佐其事——这就是所谓“得势而愈显”的榜样吧？"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "白圭经商之术",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白圭</span>是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>人。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏文侯</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李克</span>致力于尽地力的农政；白圭偏爱的却是时机——“别人丢，我就取；别人取，我就给。”年成丰熟就<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>进谷物，付出<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">丝</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">漆</span>；蚕茧上市就<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>进<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">帛絮</span>，付出粮食。他根据岁星推测年景：太岁在卯，丰年，来年反衰；至午，旱年，来年好；至酉，丰年，来年衰；至子，大旱，来年好，还有水灾。到下一轮卯位时，所<span class=\"verb-economic\" title=\"经济动词\">积</span>的货物可以比往年翻倍。想增钱财，就<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>进品质较差的谷物（价贱周转快）；想增石斗量，就取上等种子（收成好）。他生活俭朴，少吃少喝，节制嗜欲，衣服节俭，和作坊里的僮仆同甘共苦；看准时机出手，像<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">猛兽</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">挚鸟</span>扑食一样快。他自己说：“我做治生的事业，就像<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伊尹</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕尚</span>的谋划，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙武\">孙（孙武）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">吴（吴起）</span>用兵，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商鞅</span>推行法令一般。所以智不足以应变、勇不足以决断、仁不能恰当<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>予、强不能有所守——即便他要学我的方法，我也不告诉他。”因此<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>谈治生之道的都把白圭奉为鼻祖——这是经过实践检验的，他能试验而确有所长，并非空口白话。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "猗顿郭纵之富",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">猗顿</span>靠经营盬盐起家。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郭纵</span>则靠铁冶炼发家，富可敌王。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "乌氏倮与寡妇清",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">乌氏倮</span>做畜牧生意：等牲畜多了就卖掉，拿钱去买奇异的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">缯</span>织物，秘密进献给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">戎王</span>。戎王以十倍价偿还他，送给他牲畜——多得要用山谷来装<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦始皇帝</span>特令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：乌氏倮\">倮（乌氏倮）</span>比照封<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>之礼，按时和列<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>一同朝请。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">巴</span>地还有位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡妇</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：寡妇清\">清（寡妇清）</span>，她祖上发现了丹砂矿，家里独享其利<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数世（时长）</span>，家产多到算不清。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：寡妇清\">清（寡妇清）</span>虽是个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡妇</span>，却能守住祖业，以钱财保护自己，不被侵犯。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇帝\">秦皇帝（秦始皇帝）</span>认为她是贞妇，以客礼相待，还替她修了一座<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">女怀清台</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：乌氏倮\">倮（乌氏倮）</span>不过是个边地牧民之长，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：寡妇清\">清（寡妇清）</span>不过是穷乡的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡妇</span>，竟能受<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万乘</span>之君的礼遇，名扬<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>——这难道不是因为富有吗！"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "汉兴富商大贾",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兴起，海内统一，开放关卡桥梁，放宽山泽的禁令，因此富商大贾周游<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，交易的货物无所不通，得到所想要的东西，又将<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">豪杰</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>的强宗大族迁徙到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">京师</span>。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "关中巴蜀之饶",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汧</span>水、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍</span>以东直到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">华</span>山，肥沃的田野<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>，从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">虞</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>时代起就作为上等田赋，后来<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公刘</span>迁到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邠</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">大王</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王季</span>居于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">岐</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文王</span>营建<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丰</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span>治理<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">镐</span>，所以这里的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众还保有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>的遗风，喜爱稼穑，种植<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">五穀</span>，看重土地，不敢轻易做坏事。到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦文公\">文（秦文公）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦缪公\">缪（秦缪公）</span>居于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍</span>，占据<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陇蜀</span>的货物通道而多商贾。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦献公\">献公（秦献公）</span>迁都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">栎邑</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">栎邑</span>北抗<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">戎翟</span>，东通<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三晋</span>，也多大商贾。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦昭王\">昭（秦昭王）</span>治都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>，因此<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>也定都于此，即<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>和诸陵，四方车马辐凑并至会集，地小人多，所以这里的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众更加崇尚巧伪、从事商业。南边是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巴蜀</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巴蜀</span>也是沃野，富饶出产<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">卮</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">姜</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">丹沙</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">石</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">铜</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">铁</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">竹</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">木</span>之类器物。南面驾驭<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">滇僰</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">僰僮</span>奴隶之利。西近<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邛笮</span>，出产<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">笮马</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">旄牛</span>。然而四面险塞，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">栈道</span>绵延<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>，无所不通，只有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">襃斜</span>之道控扼其咽喉，用多余的物资换取稀缺之物。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天水</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陇西</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北地</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上郡</span>与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>风俗相同，然而西边有<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">羌</span>中之利，北边有<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">戎翟</span>的畜产，畜牧之盛为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之冠。然而地势也穷险，只有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">京师</span>扼其要道。所以<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>之地，占<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的三分之一，而人口不过十分之三；但是衡量它的财富，却占十分之六。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "三河与种代赵俗",
      "text": "从前<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">唐</span>人建都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河东</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>人建都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河内</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>人建都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河南</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三河</span>位于<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之中，如<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鼎</span>之三足，是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王者</span>更相居住之地，每国立国各<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数百千年（时长）</span>，土地狭小，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>人众多，是都城大国<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>聚会之地，所以这里的风俗节俭而熟于世事。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">杨</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平阳</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>地西与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">翟</span>通商，北与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">种</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>通商。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">种</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>位于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">石</span>邑之北，地邻胡人，屡遭寇侵。这里<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>人矜强凶狠，好斗意气，任侠作奸，不事农商。然而靠近<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">北夷</span>，军队常常前往，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>运输而来的物资时有盈余。这里的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众桀傲不均，自从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国时代起就忧其剽悍，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武灵王</span>又加以激励，他们的谣俗还保有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国的遗风。所以<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">杨</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平阳</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>商人就在这里往返经商，得到所想要的。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">温</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">轵</span>西与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上党</span>通商，北与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>通商。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>地薄人多，还有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沙丘</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>王淫乐之地的遗<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>，民俗急躁好斗，靠投机取利谋食。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">丈夫</span>们相聚游戏，悲歌慷慨，兴起时结伙行椎剽之事，休息时就挖墓盗宝、伪造巧诈之物，多美饰之物，从事俳优之业。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>则鼓奏<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鸣瑟</span>，穿着轻便舞鞋，游走取媚于富贵，进入后宫，遍及<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>各国。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "邯郸郑卫之俗",
      "text": "然而<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>也是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">漳</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>之间的一大都会。北通<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">涿</span>，南有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郑</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>风俗与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>相近，但靠近<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>，故稍稍持重而自矜节操。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">濮</span>上的城邑迁徙到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">野王</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">野王</span>人好斗任侠，这是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>国的遗风。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "燕地风俗",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>也是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">勃</span>海、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">碣</span>石之间的一大都会。南通<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，东北与胡人为邻。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">上谷</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">辽东</span>，地远人稀，屡遭寇侵，大体与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>俗相类，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众悍勇而少思虑，有鱼盐、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">枣</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">栗</span>之饶。北邻<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">乌桓</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">夫馀</span>，东面掌控<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">秽貉</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">朝鲜</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">真番</span>之利。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "洛阳商路",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>东与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>通商，南与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>通商。所以<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泰山</span>的南面是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>，北面是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "齐地富饶",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地背倚山海，沃野<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>，适宜<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">桑麻</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众多有<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">文采布帛</span>和<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鱼盐</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临菑</span>也是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海岱</span>之间的一大都会。其俗宽缓豁达，足智多谋，好议论，重土轻迁，怯于众斗却勇于刺杀，所以多有劫人之徒，这是大国的风气。城中士农工商贾五<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>俱全。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "邹鲁周公遗风",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邹</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>濒临<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洙</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗水</span>，还有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span>的遗风，习俗喜好<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">儒</span>学，熟悉<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>仪，所以这里的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众拘谨。颇有<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">桑麻</span>之业，没有林泽的饶产。地小人多，节俭吝啬，畏罪远邪。等到衰落以后，喜好经商逐利，比<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>人更甚。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "梁宋先王遗风",
      "text": "从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鸿沟</span>以东，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">芒</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砀</span>以北，属<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巨野</span>，这里是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">宋</span>之地。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陶</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">睢阳</span>也是一大都会。从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>兴起于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成阳</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雷泽</span>捕鱼，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>定居于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">亳</span>。这里的习俗还有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>遗风，民风厚重多<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">君子</span>，喜好稼穑，虽然没有山川之饶，却能粗<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>恶食，积蓄储藏。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "西楚风俗",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三</span>种风俗。从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>北的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汝南</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南郡</span>，这里是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">西楚</span>。其俗剽悍轻捷，容易发怒，地薄，少有积聚。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江陵</span>是从前的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郢</span>都，西通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巫</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">巴</span>，东有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">云梦</span>之饶。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>位于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>之交，流通<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鱼盐</span>之货，这里的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众多商贾。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">徐</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">僮</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">取虑</span>，则清峻刻苦，重诺守信。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "东楚江东之会",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>以东，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东海</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">广陵</span>，这里是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东楚</span>。其俗类似<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">徐</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">僮</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">朐</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">缯</span>以北，风俗就与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>相同。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">浙江</span>以南就是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>自从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">阖庐</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">春申</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王濞</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三人</span>招致<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>喜好游乐的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>弟以来，东边有<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">海盐</span>之饶，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">章山</span>之<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">铜</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三江</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">五湖</span>之利，也是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江东</span>的一大都会。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "南楚江南风物",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">衡山</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九江</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江南</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">豫章</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长沙</span>，这里是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南楚</span>，其俗大致类似<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">西楚</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">郢</span>都后来迁到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">寿春</span>，也是一大都会。而<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">合肥</span>承接南北潮水，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">皮革</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鲍</span>鱼、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">木</span>材在此集散。与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">闽中</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">干越</span>杂居，风俗混杂，所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南楚</span>人好辞令，善于游说但少诚信。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江南</span>地势低湿，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">丈夫</span>易于早夭。多<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">竹木</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">豫章</span>出产<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">黄金</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长沙</span>出产<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">连</span>（铅）、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">锡</span>，但仅有一点点产量，开采<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>得还不够成本。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九疑</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">苍梧</span>以南直至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">儋耳</span>，与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江南</span>风俗大同小异，而<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">杨越</span>人多。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">番禺</span>也是这里的一大都会，是<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">珠玑</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">犀</span>角、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玳瑁</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">果</span>品、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">布</span>匹的集散地。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "颍川南阳夏人遗风",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">颍川</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>人的居地。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>人政尚忠朴，还有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>的遗风。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">颍川</span>之人敦厚诚实。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>末世，把不法之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>迁到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>西通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武关</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郧关</span>，东南承接<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉水</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长江</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宛</span>也是一大都会。习俗驳杂好生事，业多商贾。他们任侠好义，与<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">颍川</span>相通，所以至今称他们为“<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>人”。"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "天下盐产",
      "text": "<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>物产的稀有与多寡，人<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>的谣俗，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>食<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">海盐</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山西</span>食<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">盐</span>卤，岭南、沙漠以北也往往产<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">盐</span>，大体如此。"
    },
    "26": {
      "title": "南北风土物产",
      "text": "总的来说，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>之地，地广人稀，饭食<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">稻</span>米，羹汤<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鱼</span>肉，或是火耕水耨，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">果</span>实螺蛤<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">蠃蛤</span>之类，不必交易就能自给，地势饶食，没有饥馑之患，所以偷安苟活，没有积聚而多贫。因此<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江淮</span>以南，没有挨饿受冻的人，也没有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千金</span>的富家。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沂水</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗水</span>以北，适宜<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">五穀</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">桑麻</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">六畜</span>，地小人多，屡遭水旱之灾，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众喜好积储，所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>好农而看重<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>事。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三河</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宛</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>也是如此，加以经商。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>设巧智，靠投机取利。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>从事农牧兼养蚕。"
    },
    "27": {
      "title": "百业逐利归于富",
      "text": "由此看来：贤人在庙堂上深谋远虑，在朝廷议论大政；守信死节、隐居岩穴的名士所追求的究竟是什么？归根到底，不过为了“富贵”二字。所以清廉的官吏做得久了，越久越富；廉洁的商人也趋于富贵。富贵二字，是人情所同好——不学而自然追求。"
    },
    "28": {
      "title": "素封致富之道",
      "text": "谚语说：“<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百里</span>之内不<span class=\"verb-economic\" title=\"经济动词\">贩</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">樵</span>薪，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>之内不贩<span class=\"verb-economic\" title=\"经济动词\">籴</span>粮。”居住了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年（时长）</span>，就种<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">五穀</span>；<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十年（时长）</span>，就<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">树</span>艺<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">木</span>材；<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">百年（时长）</span>，则以德行招徕人才。德，说的是人和物的归附。如今有人没有俸禄爵邑的收入，而乐趣却与有爵邑者相当。这叫做“<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">素封</span>”。封君靠食租税，每年每户收<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二百</span>钱。<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千户</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>则有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十万</span>，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">朝觐</span>聘享都由此出。庶<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>中的农工商贾，大概也每年以万钱获息<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二千</span>，所以<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百万</span>之家则有息<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十万</span>，而更役徭赋都由此出。<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>食之欲，都可以恣意享用美好的东西。所以说陆地上牧<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二百蹄</span>（五十匹），<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span>蹄角合<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span>（计一百六十七头），<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千足</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">羊</span>（二百五十只），泽中<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千足</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">彘</span>（二百五十头），水中<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千石</span>鱼陂，山中<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千章</span>大材。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">安邑</span>千株<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">树</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">枣</span>；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>千株<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">树</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">栗</span>；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉水</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江陵</span>千株<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">树</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">橘</span>；<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>北、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">常山</span>以南、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河济</span>之间千株<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">树</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">萩</span>；<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夏</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千亩</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">漆</span>；<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千亩</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">桑麻</span>；<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渭川</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千亩</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">竹</span>；以及名都<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万家</span>之城，靠近城郭的<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千亩</span>亩产一锺的良田，或<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千亩</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">卮茜</span>（染料），<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千畦</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">姜韭</span>：这些人都与<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千户</span>侯相当。这是富给的本钱，不需要窥伺市井，不需要奔走异邑，坐享其成，身有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">处士</span>之义而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>得给养。至于家贫亲老，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻</span>子软弱，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">每年按时</span>不能<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">祭祀</span>进献、合饮敬酒，饮食服饰不足以自给，如此还不羞愧，就无可比拟了。所以没有财产的人要靠力气谋生，稍有积蓄的靠智谋，已富足的争时机，这是生财的大法则。如今治生不必冒险就能<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>得收益，则贤人当勉力为之。因此以农为本致富为上，以商致富次之，靠奸诈致富最下。没有岩穴奇<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>的行为，而长期<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">贫贱</span>，却好谈<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">仁义</span>，也足以羞愧。"
    },
    "29": {
      "title": "末业致富之数",
      "text": "凡编入户籍的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众，别人富出自己十倍就对他谦卑，百倍就敬畏他，千倍就为其役使，万倍就为其仆从，这是事物的规律。要从贫困变富裕，务农不如做工，做工不如经商，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刺</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">绣文</span>不如倚门卖笑，这里说的末业，是〖◇贫者致富的凭借。在通都大邑，<span class=\"verb-economic\" title=\"经济动词\">酤</span>酒<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年（时长）</span>酿<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span>瓮，醯酱<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span>缸，浆<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span>罐，屠宰<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">羊</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">彘</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span>张皮，贩粮食<span class=\"verb-economic\" title=\"经济动词\">粜</span>出<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span>锺，柴薪<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>，船长<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千丈</span>，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">木</span>材<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span>章，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">竹</span>竿<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万</span>支，轺<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百乘</span>，牛<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span>两，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">木</span>漆器<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span>件，铜器<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千钧</span>，素木铁器或<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">卮茜</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千石</span>，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>蹄躈<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span>（约二百匹），<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千足</span>（约二百五十头），<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">羊</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">彘</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span>双，僮奴手指<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span>（约百人），<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">筋角</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">丹沙</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千斤</span>，帛絮、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">细布</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千钧</span>，文采<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千匹</span>，榻布、皮革<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千石</span>，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">漆</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千斗</span>，酒曲、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">盐</span>豉<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span>罐，鲐鱼<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千斤</span>，鲰鱼<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千石</span>，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鲍</span>鱼<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千钧</span>，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">枣栗</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千石</span>三倍，狐<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">龂</span>皮裘<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span>张，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">羔羊</span>皮裘<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千石</span>，毡席<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span>具，其他<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">果菜</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千</span>锺，放〖<span class=\"verb-economic\" title=\"经济动词\">贷</span>金钱<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千贯</span>，牵线搭桥的牙侩从中抽成，贪心的商贾可得三成利，廉谨的商贾可得五成利，这些也都可以比<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千乘</span>之家，这是大概的情况。其他杂业如果达不到二成利，就不算我所说的能致富的财路。"
    },
    "30": {
      "title": "当世贤人致富略述",
      "text": "请让我大略讲讲当世<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千里</span>之内贤人致富的事例，使后世可以借鉴选择。"
    },
    "31": {
      "title": "蜀卓氏铁冶",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>地<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卓氏</span>的先祖，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国人，靠<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">铁</span>冶炼致富。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>之后，把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卓氏</span>迁徙。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卓氏</span>被虏掠，只有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻</span>推着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">辇</span>车，前往迁徙之地。其他被迁的虏者稍有余财，就争相贿赂官吏，求在近处安置，被安置在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">葭萌</span>。唯独<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卓氏</span>说：“此地狭薄。我听说<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汶山</span>脚下，有沃野，地里产<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">蹲鸱</span>（大芋头），人到死都不会挨饿。当地<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众擅长市场交易，容易经商。”于是请求远迁。被迁到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临邛</span>，大喜，随即在<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">铁</span>山鼓风冶铸，运筹谋划，倾动<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">滇蜀</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>，富有到僮仆达<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千人</span>。田池射猎之乐，比拟于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>。"
    },
    "32": {
      "title": "程郑冶铸",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程郑</span>，是从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>迁徙来的虏民，也从事冶铸，卖给椎髻的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众（西南夷），财富可与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卓氏</span>相等，都居住在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">临邛</span>。"
    },
    "33": {
      "title": "宛孔氏铁冶",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宛</span>地<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔氏</span>的先祖，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>人，以<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">铁</span>冶炼为业。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>之时，把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔氏</span>迁到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>。大规模鼓风冶铸，规划陂池，连结<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车骑</span>，游历于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，因而通得商贾之利，有游闲<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>馈赠的美名。然而他的盈利超过常规，胜过那些纤啬者，家中致富<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千金</span>，所以<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南阳</span>的商贾都效法<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔氏</span>的雍容气度。"
    },
    "34": {
      "title": "鲁曹邴氏俭啬",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>人风俗俭啬，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹邴氏</span>尤其如此，靠<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">铁</span>冶炼起家，富至巨万。然而他家自<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>兄到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>孙都立下约定：俯下身子就要拾取东西，抬起头就要<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>利，以<span class=\"verb-economic\" title=\"经济动词\">贳贷</span>和行贾遍及郡国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邹</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>地方因此多有抛弃<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">文学</span>而追逐利益的人，这都是因为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曹邴氏</span>的影响。"
    },
    "35": {
      "title": "刀间使奴致富",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地风俗贱视奴虏，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刀间</span>独独爱重他们。那些凶悍狡黠的奴仆，是别人所忧虑的，唯独<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刀间</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>用他们，派他们去追逐<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">渔盐</span>商贾之利，有的连结<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车骑</span>，与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">守相</span>交结，然而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刀间</span>更加信任他们。最终得到他们的效力，起家富至<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千万</span>。所以有俗语说“宁可不要封爵，也不要离开<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刀间\">刀（刀间）</span>家”，说的是他能让桀骜的奴仆自己致富而竭尽其力。"
    },
    "36": {
      "title": "师史转毂致富",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>人本来就纤细精打细算，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">师史</span>尤其如此，他用来周转的车有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百</span>辆之多，经商于郡国之间，无所不至。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>地处<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐秦楚赵</span>之中，贫人在<span class=\"verb-economic\" title=\"经济动词\">富</span>家学做事，相互夸耀做生意日久，屡次经过自己的城邑都不回家，他就交给这种人任事，所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">师史</span>能<span class=\"verb-economic\" title=\"经济动词\">致</span>富<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七千万</span>。"
    },
    "37": {
      "title": "宣曲任氏窖粟",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">宣曲</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任氏</span>的先祖，是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">督道仓吏</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>亡之时，豪杰都争相<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金玉</span>，唯独<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任氏</span>储藏仓粟于窖中。后来<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>对峙，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众不能耕种，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">米</span>每石值万钱，而豪杰的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金玉</span>尽归<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任氏</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任氏</span>因此起家致富。富人们争相奢侈，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任氏</span>折节俭约，致力于田畜。田畜之事，别人都争相<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>低价货物，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">任氏</span>独独<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>昂贵的上等货。家族富了好几代。然而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：任氏\">任公（任氏）</span>家约定：不是田畜所产出的不穿不吃，公事没完成则自己不得饮<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>吃<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">肉</span>。以此作为乡里的表率，所以富而受<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">主上</span>敬重。"
    },
    "38": {
      "title": "无盐氏子钱之富",
      "text": "边塞开放之时，只有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桥姚</span>已拥有<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千匹</span>，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span>加倍，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">羊</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万头</span>，粮食以万锺计。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴楚七国</span>起兵时，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>城中的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>封<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>从军出征，向放息钱家借贷子<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钱</span>（利钱），放贷的子<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钱</span>家认为侯邑封国都在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关东</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关东</span>胜<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>未定，不肯借贷。只有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无盐氏</span>拿出<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千金</span>借贷，利息十倍。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三月（时长）</span>之后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴楚</span>平定，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年（时长）</span>之中，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">无盐氏</span>获息十倍，因此富可比<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>。"
    },
    "39": {
      "title": "关中田氏诸富家",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>的富商大贾，大多出自诸<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田</span>家，如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田啬</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田兰</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">韦家</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗氏</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">安陵</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">杜</span>县的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">杜氏</span>，也都财富巨万。"
    },
    "40": {
      "title": "富无经业",
      "text": "这些都是富人中最显著特异的。他们都不是靠爵邑奉禄或舞弄法令犯奸而致富，而是都努力趋避得失、与时俯仰，获取盈利，以末业致财，用本业守之，用武力一决胜负，用文才维持局面，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">变化</span>有法度，所以值得称道。至于那些致力于农耕畜牧、工匠虞人、商贾经营，凭借权利而致富，大者富倾一郡，中者富倾一县，下者富倾乡里的，不可胜数。"
    },
    "41": {
      "title": "奇业致富之例",
      "text": "纤啬经营、勤劳筋力，是治生的正道，然而富者必定要靠出奇制胜。田农，是笨拙之业，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦扬</span>靠它冠盖一州。掘坟，是奸邪之事，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田叔</span>靠它起家。博戏，是恶业，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桓发</span>靠它致富。行贾，是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">丈夫</span>之贱行，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">雍乐成</span>靠它致饶。贩卖脂膏，是辱贱之处，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">雍伯</span>获<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千金</span>。卖浆水，是小业，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张氏</span>获<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千万</span>。洒削（磨刀），是薄技，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郅氏</span>得以<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鼎</span>食（钟鸣鼎食）。卖胃脯，是简易微末之业，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">浊氏</span>得以连骑出行。<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>医，是浅薄方术，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张里</span>得以<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">锺</span>享乐。这些都是由诚心专一所致。"
    },
    "42": {
      "title": "素封结论",
      "text": "由此看来，致富没有固定的行业，钱财也没有固定的主人，能者像车辐聚拢一样归于一方，不肖者如瓦片碎裂一样分散。<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千金</span>之家可比一都的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>主，拥有巨万者就与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王者</span>同乐。这难道就是所谓的“<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">素封</span>”吗？还是不是呢？"
    },
    "43": {
      "title": "赞文",
      "text": "货殖的利益，是从工商经营而来。<span class=\"verb-economic\" title=\"经济动词\">废居</span>（囤积待售）善于积储，倚市而求利。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">白圭</span>之策能富国，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">计然</span>之策能强兵。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：乌氏倮\">倮（乌氏倮）</span>得以参加朝请之礼，女子（<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：寡妇清\">清（寡妇清）</span>）获建怀清之台。素封千户，名显于世——其由来可稽。"
    }
  }
}